Package jsocket.socket

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectSocket
    Abstracts StringSocket implemntations to handle complex objects instead of strings It is suggested that implementation extend StringSocketImpl
    Socket
    Wraps a Socket and simply sends and receives bytes Base interface for this package Lowest level in abstraction
    StringSocket
    Abstracts Socket implementations to handle strings instead of byte arrays It is suggested that implementation extend SocketImpl
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ObjectSocketImpl
    Abstracts StringSocket implemntations to handle complex objects instead of strings It is suggested that implementation extend StringSocketImpl Default implementation
    SocketImpl
    Wraps a Socket and simply sends and receives bytes Base class for this subpackage Lowest level in abstraction
    StringSocketImpl
    Abstracts Socket implementations to handle strings instead of byte arrays It is suggested that implementation extend SocketImpl
